The shrine does not have a resident Shinto priest ({{ill|Shinto Priest|ja|神職|12=draft|12=draft}}) and is concurrently served by [http://www.kanagawa-jinja.or.jp/search_dtl.php4?jid=359&cd=1203043&scd=000&npg=0 八幡社] located in {{ill|Hodogaya Ward|ja|保土ケ谷区|12=draft|12=draft}}, Setoketani Town.

