== Festivals and Annual Events ==
* {{ill|Festival|ja|festival|lt=Reitaisai|lt_ja=例大祭|qq=draft|qq=draft}}：{{ill|October 9|ja|10月9日|qq=draft|qq=draft}} (Autumn Grand Festival)

== Other Information ==
The shrine does not have a resident Shinto priest ({{ill|Shinto Priest|ja|神職|qq=draft|qq=draft}}) and is concurrently served by [http://www.kanagawa-jinja.or.jp/search_dtl.php4?jid=359&cd=1203043&scd=000&npg=0 八幡社] located in {{ill|Hodogaya Ward|ja|保土ケ谷区|qq=draft|qq=draft}}, Setoketani Town.

== Location and Access ==
{{ill|Kanagawa Prefecture|ja|神奈川県|qq=draft|qq=draft}}{{ill|Yokohama City|ja|横浜市|qq=draft|qq=draft}}{{ill|Kohoku Ward|ja|港北区|qq=draft|qq=draft}}{{ill|Shinyoshida Town|ja|新吉田町|qq=draft|qq=draft}}4509
* A 15–20 minute walk from {{ill|Hokuyamada Station|ja|東山田駅|qq=draft|qq=draft}} on the {{ill|Yokohama Municipal Subway Green Line|ja|横浜市営地下鉄グリーンライン|qq=draft|qq=draft}}

