== Other Information ==
The shrine does not have a resident Shinto priest ([[:en:Kannushi|Shinto Priest]]) and is concurrently served by [http://www.kanagawa-jinja.or.jp/search_dtl.php4?jid=359&cd=1203043&scd=000&npg=0 八幡社] located in [[:en:Hodogaya-ku, Yokohama|Hodogaya Ward]], Setoketani Town.

