== Other Information ==
The shrine does not have a resident Shinto priest ([[:en:Kannushi|Shinto Priest]]) and is concurrently served by [http://www.kanagawa-jinja.or.jp/search_dtl.php4?jid=359&cd=1203043&scd=000&npg=0 八幡社] located in {{ill|Hodogaya-ku, Yokohama|en|Hodogaya-ku, Yokohama|WD=Q1192964|lt=Hodogaya Ward}}, Setoketani Town.

