* {{ill|Associated Deities|ja|deity#主神・配神|lt=Associated Deities|lt_ja=配祀神|12=simple|13=User:Immanuelle/Associated Deities|ja_comment=jawiki link invalid}}: {{ill|Kamakura Gongorō Kagemasa|en|Kamakura Gongorō Kagemasa|WD=Q1154948|lt=Gongorō Kagemasa}}, {{ill|Hino Seibyō|ja|比野聖廟|12=simple|13=User:Immanuelle/Hino Seibyō|ja_comment=jawiki link invalid}}, {{ill|Susanoo|1=Susanoo-no-Mikoto|ja|素戔嗚尊|12=simple|13=User:Immanuelle/Susanoo|13=User:Immanuelle/Susanoo-no-Mikoto|ja_comment=jawiki redirects to スサノオ}}<ref name="kamnavi-shinyoshida-sugiyama">[http://kamnavi.jp/it/musasi/indexy.htm#khayabu1 武蔵の五十猛命 神奈川県横浜市：新吉田町　杉山神社]（神奈備）</ref>
